verses.rendering:
You will prophesy all these words against them and say to them:

The LORD roars from on high;
from his holy dwelling he thunders.
He roars fiercely against his fold;
he shouts like those who tread the grapes
against all the inhabitants of the earth.

This is what the LORD of Hosts says:
Disaster is spreading from nation to nation;
a great storm is stirring from the farthest corners of the earth.
